### step 1: parse the voice transcript
POST http://localhost:3000/api/calendar/intent
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transcript": "schedule a linear algebra review for tomorrow at 2pm for 90 minutes"
}

###

### step 2: confirm
POST http://localhost:3000/api/calendar/confirm
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": {
    "action": "calendar",
    "summary": "Schedule a 90-minute Linear Algebra review tomorrow at 2pm",
    "payload": {
      "title": "Linear Algebra Review",
      "start": "2026-05-29T14:00:00",
      "end": "2026-05-29T15:30:00",
      "description": "Focus session covering eigenvalues and eigenvectors",
      "location": null
    }
  }
}

###

